        {
          "type": "text",
          "body": "Card Guardians needed an engaging App Preview video to boost performance in paid ad campaigns. The goal was to increase CTR (clickthrough rate).\n\n**The Approach**\n\nTo stand out in crowded mobile game ads, the focus was combining authentic gameplay with cinematic visual effects — fast-paced editing, dynamic camera cuts, and synchronized VFX/SFX.\n\n**The Result**\n\nThe final motion was designed in multiple formats (vertical, horizontal and square), all under 30 seconds."
